    "longBusinessSummary": "Bentre Aquaproduct Import and Export Joint Stock Company engages in the farming, processing, and exporting seafood in Vietnam. It offers Pangasius fish, and white, yellow, and hard-shell clams. The company exports its products primarily to Japan, the United States, the European Union, Canada, Australia, Singapore, South Korea, Hong Kong, and China. The company was formerly known as Bentre Frozen Aquaproduct Export Company and changed its name to Bentre Aquaproduct Import and Export Joint Stock Company in December 2003. The company was founded in 1977 and is headquartered in Vinh Long, Vietnam. Bentre Aquaproduct Import and Export Joint Stock Company operates as a subsidiary of The PAN Group Joint Stock Company.",
